AIpower charter documents — License / 许可协议

All documentation, charter texts, manifestos, and other written materials in
this repository are licensed under the Creative Commons
Attribution-ShareAlike 4.0 International License (CC BY-SA 4.0).

本仓库中所有文档、章程文本、宣言及其他书面材料，
采用知识共享 署名-相同方式共享 4.0 国际许可协议（CC BY-SA 4.0）发布。

You are free to:
  * Share — copy and redistribute the material in any medium or format
  * Adapt — remix, transform, and build upon the material for any purpose,
    even commercially

Under the following terms:
  * Attribution — You must give appropriate credit to AIpower,
    provide a link to the license, and indicate if changes were made.
  * ShareAlike — If you remix, transform, or build upon the material,
    you must distribute your contributions under the same license.

Full legal text:
