NOTE FOR FUTURE CODE / 关于未来代码的说明

When AIpower working groups publish code (e.g. access tools, evaluation
scripts, mirror infrastructure), each such sub-project may carry its own
OSI-approved open-source license (recommended: Apache-2.0 or MIT) declared
in that sub-project's own LICENSE file.

当 AIpower 工作组发布代码（如访问工具、评测脚本、镜像基础设施）时，
每个子项目可在其自身 LICENSE 文件中声明独立的、OSI 认可的开源许可协议
（推荐：Apache-2.0 或 MIT）。
